---------------------------------
Type of css
---------------------------------

    syntax ->
         selctor 
            {
             property : value ;
             property : value ;
            }

1. inline css (same line)
2. internal css
3. External css

---------------------------------
Type of selector 
---------------------------------

1. element selector (tag name)
2. Id selctor (#)
3. class selctor (.class)
4. Univarsal selctor (*)
5. Descendant selctor (space)
6. child selctor (>)
7. attribute selector (input[Type=" "])
8. grouping selector (selctor,selector)

---------------------------------
css colors
---------------------------------

1. colorname
2. hexa code
3. rgb(0 to 255)

---------------------------------
BackGround-rules
---------------------------------

1. BackGround color
colorname #hexaCode rgb()

2. BackGround-image
url("imageName")

3. BackGround-repeat
repeat-x repeat-y no-repeat

MCQ
note : shortHand
BackGround = pink url("i.jpg") repeat-x

---------------------------------
css text Manipulation
---------------------------------

1. text-indent
--> by defualt value is 0
--> negitive values are allowed

2. text-decoration
--> none 
--> overline
--> underline
--> line-through

3. text-transform
--> none 
--> uppercase
--> lowercase
--> capitalize

4. text-align
--> left(by defualt)
--> right
--> center
--> justify

---------------------------------
css Fonts
---------------------------------

1. font-family

2. font-style
--> normal 
--> italic

3. font-weight
--> normal 
--> bold

4. font-variant
--> normal 
--> small-caps

5. font-size
--> medium 
--> small 
--> x-small 
--> xx-small
--> large
--> x-large
--> xx-large
--> px
--> %

---------------------------------
css text controls
---------------------------------
--> letter-spacing
--> word-spacing

---------------------------------
css borders
---------------------------------

1. border-style
- solid - dotted - dashed - double

2. border-width
- px,pt,cm,em
- pre-defina
    - thin thic medium

3. border-color
colorname rgb() #hexaCode

4. border-radius
- px
- % 

---------------------------------
css borders
---------------------------------

--> pseudo class 
1. :link 
2. :visited
3. :hover
4. :active 
5. :focus 
6. :nth child(n)
7. :not(selector)
8. :checked

--> syntex 

selector:pseudoclass
{
    property : value;
}


---------------------------------
pseudo elements
---------------------------------

::first-line
::first-letter
::befor
::marker 
::selection

syntext :
selector::pseudo-element 
{
    proparty:value
}

---------------------------------
text proparty
---------------------------------

1. line-height 
    -> px , %
    px , %
    -> normal
note -> negitive value are not allowed

2. text-shadow

text-shadow: 2px epx 5px red



